      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start. Can you expand more on the Mill angle? Specifically, how would someone using his framework argue that even \"harmful\" or \"misinformation\" content shouldn't be regulated by the state? I want to make the case that the \"marketplace of ideas\" is the only legitimate way to handle bad speech.",
